# Large raw Kaplan UCR data (multi-GB; user-downloaded from openICPSR project 100707).
# The processed data/processed/county_crime_*.csv files are committed instead;
# rebuild from raw with: python scripts/build_county_crime.py
data/county/kaplan_offenses/

# Kaplan LEOKA / Police-Employee data (openICPSR project 102180; user must
# download — login required). Drop the .zip in here as-is; the build script
# streams the inner CSV directly via Python's zipfile module without unzipping.
# Rebuild with: python scripts/build_county_leoka.py
data/county/kaplan_leoka/

# State CJ raw downloads (BJS Prisoners reports, Census State&Local Finance
# summary tables, DPIC executions database). Many files are PDFs and large
# zips; the processed data/processed/state_cj_controls_*.csv files are
# committed instead. Rebuild raw set + processed CSVs with:
#   python scripts/build_state_cj_controls.py
data/state_cj_raw/

